      <title>拜登将在援助人员死亡引发的紧张局势中与内塔尼亚胡交谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/biden-to-speak-with-netanyahu-as-tensions-flare-over-aid-deaths</link>
